{"tid":2020901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《地厚天高》現已登陸 iTunes Store","createTime":"2020-05-17T11:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T12:01:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff03ff9bca492cc59cd5ed0ecd07b52587109c1","tid":2020901,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"【《地厚天高》現已登陸 iTunes Store】<br />\n【&quot;Lost in the Fumes&quot; now available on iTunes Store】<br />\n<br />\n立即看： <a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e615KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=bc04fef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a><br />\n<br />\n經過多月的努力，《地厚天高》終於在50個國家上架 iTunes Store。一直以來，我們聽到不少觀眾的反映，希望能簡易地觀看數位高清版本的《地厚天高》。在家裡沒有DVD機、海外的朋友，機會來了！<br />\n<br />\n按以下鏈結或直接於 iTunes 搜尋「Lost In The Fumes」就可以立即串流觀看《地厚天高》！最後，多謝影意志各合作單位的努力，讓這部紀錄片可以走出香港，讓世界各地的更多朋友得悉香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Lost in the Fumes&quot; is now available internationally on iTunes Store on more than 50 countries! For all of you who don't have a DVD player or cannot get the DVD locally, you can now watch the documentary in the comfort of your own home with the newly released digital version. <br />\n<br />\nWe would also like to thank our distributor Ying E Chi for all the efforts that made this possible. Click in the following link for purchase or rental:  <a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e615KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=bc04fef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a><br />\n<br />\n#地厚天高 #iTunes #LostInTheFumes"},{"pid":"7b5cf7f049754caaa5b4e6ab829cbbb99306b940","tid":2020901,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"課佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持天琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人可以為左湄公河而爆seed，咁今日可唔可以為左自己而爆seed?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2020376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2020376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f6da70220373aca3b57cc2cc55a004b9ffed0ee","tid":2020901,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尚欠90%！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQt3hkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQt3hkf.jpg&h=d8fea6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌連結</span>：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e615KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=004fd9c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n來源（區議員認證）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1162995320709549/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F915080692167681%2Fposts%2F1162995320709549%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e615KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=65f07e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1162995320709549/</a><br />\n<br />\n#借位"},{"pid":"772c89c07c91d3c575b4f25bc03a3d286eab5345","tid":2020901,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiV9dij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiV9dij.png&h=e814fadf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"969e437829d5d6bc2c8dd558769b793988937c54","tid":2020901,"uid":45753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"772c89c07c91d3c575b4f25bc03a3d286eab5345","tid":2020901,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiV9dij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi